  Version bump. Respect CFLAGS and LDFLAGS.

*msn-pecan-0.1.0_rc1-r1 (24 Dec 2009)

  24 Dec 2009; Peter Volkov <pva@gentoo.org> -msn-pecan-0.1.0_rc1.ebuild,
